Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.89,0:00:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Double Ranger Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! That's not fair...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You should fall down if you get kicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The evil emperor who plots world conquest...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.86,0:00:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot be defeated that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that at the end of those TV\Nshows the bad guys always lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your world conquest coming along smoothly?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't go down, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, the hard part comes\Nafter you conquer the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of world do you plan to build?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:00:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll leave it messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds more fun if you're\Njust going to mess it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quitting the Rainbow Rangers\Nand joining the Evil Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we all head back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head back now.\NDon't forget anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:17.23,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(360,340)}Just One Case
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotten warmer lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Rosemary?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't catch a cold this\Nwinter, did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she did. She was running around\Nwith her friends outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She always did get a bad\Nfever every winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was around this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We took her to the doctor in\Nthe middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You carry around an album of her pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.27,0:03:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have grown so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Since she's still growing, I wonder if her face has\Nchanged in the little while that I've not seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have confidence that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how old Rosemary gets,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be able to recognize her instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes,\Nplease show this to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It contains copies of the report\Nand newspaper clippings...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,from when I shot the young boy, the\Nperpetrator of the serial killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not telling you to explain\Nthings clearly to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fact that I killed a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to defend myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want her to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder... when I can see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask her again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,whether or not she wants to see her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:04:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home every night by nine o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You've really returned to how you used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Those youthful eyes that you had when\Nyou were a rookie detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, much like the time when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:26.92,Default,,0,0,30,,So how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:30.38,Default,,0,0,30,,There are benefits if you sign up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:34.80,Default,,0,0,6,,The thing is, we're already signed up\Nwith another insurance company.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:32.56,Location,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Offenbach\NHesse
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you here, Mr. Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The insurance we have now is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have the extra money to\Npay for more insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We got our insurance right when\Nwe moved here four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Four years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you live before coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In Brunt치l, near Mannheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Brunt치l? That's a nice area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you born there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we lived there up until we moved here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, ma'am, do you have any kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. My son is currently at the\NUniversity of Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? He's a college student?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,then I have the perfect policy for\Na young man like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please listen to what I'm offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks like he was a cute one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What is his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, please don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since he went to the\NUniversity of Munich,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,we've only gotten a call from\Nhim once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys are like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I went there, Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, to Johan's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was a family just like any other,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,with absolutely nothing out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you think, Richard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, from my analysis as an ex-detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the more ordinary something seems,\Nthe more suspect it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I'll continue investigating\NJohan's surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's got to be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,At the gymnasium that Johan\Nattended, he had a reputation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of being a good student with\Ngood grades and conduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have confidence that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how old Rosemary gets,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be able to recognize her instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't imagine how that baby's face\Ncan become Johan's adult face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:32.84,Location,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}Brunt치l City Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the birth certificate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Johan Wilhelm Liebert.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Born on February 9th, 1976.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was indeed born in this city.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's absolutely nothing out of the ordinary...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:08:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hertz!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no smoking in the City Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that... Go get me an ashtray.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember that there was a\Nfire here four years ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All the paperwork was destroyed.\NIt was a big mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you guys redo all the\Npaperwork back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The paperwork was redone according\Nto individual request,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but since this is such a small city, most\Nof the paperwork was restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thanks for coming, Dr. Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma went to you and told you he\Nwas looking for a man named Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no basis for his story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:10:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But if this person was indeed the\Nfriend who led the serial killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Peter Jurgens, whom I was researching, astray,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,then it would be a breakthrough for all the cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Dr. Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll get permission to see\NJurgens as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Depending on how he reacts to this photo,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,we might be able to prove\NDr. Tenma's innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He died?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The real Johan, who was born in\NBrunt치l, died when he was two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that the Liebert couple\Nused the fire as an opportunity...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to reissue documents that said\Nthat he was still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the person who's called\NJohan Liebert is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,as I told you before, I gave\NJohan's photo to Dr. Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully an answer will come out of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How about some food?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I have to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:12:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You've been running around all\Nday and you still have work to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I may get a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be able to see my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The important thing is to move forward, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent, you've made a full recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad? It's me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosemary...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We can meet... anytime you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Richard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about this young boy, Jurgens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you recognize him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Might you have met him before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned that your friend, Johan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,never met you personally,\Nbut only wrote you letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan knew you pretty well, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I borrow a pen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm not allowed to\Nhand you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A pen, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The park.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At the park,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the day after I killed somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's stop this."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's stop right here."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that as I went to the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a lot of children with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you wait a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to start the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you start from the beginning again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"You should come, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"You should come, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"You should come, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"You should come, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"You should come, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"You should..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We met at Mr. Schubert's, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Johan Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I called you many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but you never picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I came to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Gillen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it go when you showed\Nthe photo to Jurgens?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He died?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he just died in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to the police questioning, I\Ncan't leave the hospital either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of my negligence,\NI gave him a pen, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,an important witness has...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Dr. Reichwein,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,his suicide was no doubt a\Nreaction to Johan's picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as the questioning ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll head over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll contact Richard right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A research paper for your university?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm researching the UN Convention\Nof 1989 on the Rights of the Child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like a drink, Mr. Richard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that you've stopped drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you were drunk when\Nyou executed that young boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I was drunk at the time,\NI did something inexcusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'd like to ask you about...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The young boy you killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stephan Joss, seventeen years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What crime did he commit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A young boy, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That seventeen-year-old "young boy"\Ncommitted such horrible crimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine rape-homicides and two homicides!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why you executed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't an execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, you know that under Article 40 of\Nthe UN Convention on the Rights of the Child,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,a child is "innocent until proven guilty," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was once with the Juvenile Division, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you know that under Article 37, a person\Nunder eighteen cannot be executed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,or sentenced to life in prison for\Ncrimes that they've committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the Convention consists of basic rights\Nthat are granted to all in this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,be it a child or an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My shooting him was not an execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a mistake caused by alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I did something inexcusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm now being sanctioned by society...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, please wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to meet you for my paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If I've offended you, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we take a walk to change the mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like this whiskey, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the winds at night are chilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Dr. Gillen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't get a hold of Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me he might be able to\Nmeet his daughter, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he's out meeting\Nher this late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, please tell him to be\Ncareful when you reach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading over there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know Stephan Joss's record?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, when he was young,\Nhe was in an East Berlin orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to know more about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important if you want to know\Nwhere he's coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The orphanage he was in...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a horrible place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He was truly a nice boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one knows what kinds of horrible things\Nhappened to him at that orphanage...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,or just how badly his spirit was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Convention on the Rights of the Child, Article 6,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the right to life, and guaranteed\Nsurvival and development.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Article 8, the right to preserve one's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Article 19, protection from child abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, those things were not provided\Nfor them in that hellish place...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,at 511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to meet your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that your daughter on the\Nphone back at your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to meet her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To write a paper for my university.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Your purpose for being with Schubert now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you shot the boy\Nbecause you were drunk, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, answer my question!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that on that day, you were seen drinking\Nin a bar after shooting that young boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But something's amiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,According to my research, there wasn't a single person\Nwho saw you drinking before you shot that young boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be possible that you weren't drunk\Nwhen you shot that young boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You were sober.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You were calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You calmly pulled the trigger because\Nyou wanted to execute him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you just lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just lying to others...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,or just to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you confirm that young boy's crimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have the right to execute him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that just by pretending,\Nyour sins would go away?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What a heavy sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How can one who has committed such a sin... meet his\Ndaughter as though he's made a complete comeback?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you have a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Gillen?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Dr. Gillen?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your patient, Richard Braun, is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:53.53,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(360,340)}Decision
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.12,0:22:36.79,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And slowly, you come to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:44.38,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's all as it should be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:53.81,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You can only do so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:22:59.40,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If you're game enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.82,0:23:07.20,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You could place your trust in me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:16.29,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For the love of life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:21.63,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}There's a trade off
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:28.39,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We could lose it all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:33.31,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But we'll go down fighting

